Set Nettle$Dir <Obey$Dir>
IconSprites <Nettle$Dir>.!Sprites

Set Nettle$ZapRedraw Loaded
RMEnsure ZapRedraw 0.00 Set Nettle$ZapRedraw NotLoaded

Set Nettle$ZapRedrawPath <Zap$Redraw>
If "<Nettle$ZapRedrawPath>"="" Then Set Nettle$ZapRedrawPath <Nettle$Dir>.Resources.ZapRedraw
If "<Nettle$ZapRedraw>"="NotLoaded" Then RMLoad <Nettle$ZapRedrawPath>

Unset Nettle$ZapRedraw
Unset Nettle$ZapRedrawPath

RMEnsure Resolver 0.49 RMLoad System:Modules.Network.Resolver
RMEnsure Resolver 0.49 Error Nettle requires Resolver 0.49 or later

Set Alias$@RunType_FD3 DebugAIF %*0

WimpSlot -min 256K -max 256K
Run <Nettle$Dir>.!RunImage ><Nettle$Dir>.stdout 2><Nettle$Dir>.stderr